<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer1617150510090466438">The 14th century gives us back two contradictory images: a glittering time of crusades and castles, cathedrals and chivalry, and a dark time of ferocity and spiritual agony, a world plunged into a chaos of war, fear and the Plague. <b>Barbara Tuchman</b> anatomizes the century, revealing both the great rhythms of history and the grain and texture of domestic life as it was lived.</span>

      </div>
